text:
Personality... What is my personality...!?
Hmm... Since chocolate and sweets are external...

Ah, Rinze-chan! You know, I was thinking...
Our group has such unique personalities, right...?

Compared to everyone,
I'm just an ordinary high school girl~...!

Really!? Where, where!?
Where do you think my personality is!? Tell me!
...It's difficult to put into words immediately...

R-Really!? That's it, that's it! My personality...
is rich in emotions! Emotions... rich in emotions...
